jwt a way to encode info
JWT.encode({beef: "yo"}, "supersecretkey")
JWT.encode({user_id: 2}, "supersecretkey")
a=_  (get last result)
jwt.decode(a, "supersecretkey")
*using this for user_id being sent to front end

this will be done in application controller

def encode(payload)
  JWT.encode(payload, "arbi")
end
def decode(jwt)
  JWT.decode(jwt, "arbi")[0]
end
